####################
# 5: Mouse and Key bindings
#
# Contexts:
#     R = Root Window                 rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#     W = Application Window          rIrrrr<---------^rrrrr
#     F = Frame Corners               rrrrrr[13TTTT642]rrrrr
#     S = Frame Sides                 rIrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     T = Title Bar                   rrrrrr[wwwwwwwww]rrrrr
#     I = Icon                        rIrrrrv_________>rrrrr
#                                     rrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
#
#     Numbers are buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#
# Modifiers: (A)ny, (C)ontrol, (S)hift, (M)eta, (N)othing
#
# Format: Key <X>  <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
#         Mouse <X> <Context> <Modifier> <Action>
#
# Silent supresses any errors (such as keyboards with no Menu key).
####################

# Window Buttons: [1 3 5 7 9  TTTTT  0 8 6 4 2]
#   1 - Close on single click, Destory on double click.
#   3 - Iconify (minimize)
#   5 - Maximize (right/middle button will only maximize vertical/horizontal)
Mouse 1 1 A Delete
Mouse 1 3 A Thumbnail
Mouse 1 5 A FvwmMaximize 100 100
Mouse 2 5 A FvwmMaximize 0 100
Mouse 3 5 A FvwmMaximize 100 0

#   TitleBar: Click to Raise, Move, Double Click to Maximize
#             Mouse Wheel Up/Down to WindowShade On/Off
#   Borders: Click to raise, Move to Resize
#   Root Window: Left Click - Main Menu
#                Right Click - WindowOps Menu
#                Middle Click - Window List Menu
#   Right click TitleBar/Borders for WindowOps Menu
Mouse 1	T    A RaiseMoveX Move Maximize
Mouse 1	FS   A RaiseMove Resize
Mouse 4 T    A FvwmWindowShade False
Mouse 5 T    A FvwmWindowShade True
Mouse 1 R    A Menu FvwmRootMenu
Mouse 2	R    A WindowList
Mouse 3 R    A Menu FvwmOpsMenu
Mouse 1	I    A RaiseMoveX Move "Iconify off"
Mouse 3	T    A Menu MenuWindowOps
Mouse 1 WT 4 FvwmMove
Mouse 3 WT 4 FvwmResize
Mouse 1 A C4 Scroll reverse

# Simple Commands
Silent Key Super_L  A     A       FvwmLaunch
Silent Key Super_R  A     A       FvwmLaunch
Silent Key Menu     A     A       FvwmRootMenu
Silent Key Return   A     4       FvwmTerm
Silent Key Return   A     4S      FvwmEditor
Silent Key Space    A     4       FvwmLaunch
Silent Key E        A     4       FvwmFileManager
